sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Customer
    participant UI as Mobile/Web App
    participant BFF as Web/Mobile BFF
    participant Orch as Onboarding Orchestrator
    participant CIS as Customer Info Service
    participant Doc as Document Service
    participant IDV as IDV Service
    participant Risk as Risk & Compliance
    participant CoreAdapter as Account Creation Service
    participant Kafka as Event Backbone
    participant CoreBank as Core Banking
    participant Notif as Notification Service

    Note over Customer, Orch: 1. Start Onboarding & Capture Details
    Customer->>UI: Starts onboarding journey
    UI->>BFF: POST /onboarding
    BFF->>Orch: Route request
    Orch-->>UI: 201 Created (sessionId)

    Customer->>UI: Enters personal details
    UI->>Orch: PUT /onboarding/{sessionId}/personal-details
    Orch->>CIS: Validate & stage data
    CIS-->>Orch: Validation successful
    Orch-->>UI: 200 OK

    Note over Customer, Doc: 2. Document Upload
    Customer->>UI: Uploads ID card & face scan
    UI->>Orch: POST /onboarding/{sessionId}/documents
    Orch->>Doc: Securely store ID and selfie
    Doc-->>Orch: Storage confirmed
    Orch-->>UI: 200 OK

    Note over UI, Risk: 3. Automated Verification Checks
    UI->>Orch: POST /onboarding/{sessionId}/verify
    Orch-->>UI: 202 Accepted (VERIFICATION_PENDING)
    
    par Verification
        Orch->>IDV: Trigger OCR, liveness, face match
        IDV-->>Orch: Verified
    and Compliance
        Orch->>Risk: Trigger AML/PEP screening
        Risk-->>Orch: Verified
    end

    Note over Orch, CoreAdapter: 4. Profile & Account Creation
    Orch->>CIS: Create golden record of customer
    CIS-->>Orch: Profile created

    Orch->>CoreAdapter: Request account creation
    CoreAdapter->>Kafka: Publish account.requested (topic-account-events)
    CoreAdapter-->>Orch: 202 Accepted (ACCOUNT_CREATION_PENDING)
    
    Note over Kafka, CoreBank: 5. Async Core Banking Processing
    Kafka->>CoreBank: Consume account.requested
    CoreBank->>Kafka: Publish account.opened (topic-account-events)
    
    Note over Kafka, Notif: 6. Completion & Notification State Change
    Kafka->>Orch: Consume account.opened
    Note over Orch: Update session state to COMPLETED
    Orch->>Kafka: Publish onboarding.status.changed (topic-onboarding-events)
    
    Kafka->>Notif: Consume onboarding.status.changed
    Notif-->>Customer: Send Welcome Email/SMS
    
    UI->>Orch: GET /onboarding/{sessionId}/status
    Orch-->>UI: 200 OK (Status: COMPLETED)
    UI-->>Customer: Display "Your new account is ready!"